584
01:09:59,380 --> 01:10:02,380
[SPEAKER_01] Na naš račun, rekla bih i na račun naših života.

585
01:10:02,380 --> 01:10:03,039
[SPEAKER_01] A nismo ta sredstva.

586
01:10:03,039 --> 01:10:04,579
[SPEAKER_01] Nismo ta sredstva, da.

587
01:10:04,579 --> 01:10:10,100
